    h2 Who can contribute?
    p Anyone with the drive to improve our community and the will to collaborate with others can contribute to Code for Fort Lauderdale.
    p We welcome coders, writers, designers, idea-makers, leaders, followers, project managers, sponsors, entrepreneurs, restaurateurs, donors and anyone willing to contribute something to making our city better.

    h2 How can you contribute?
    p The possibilities for contributing to Code for Fort Lauderdale are endless, but here are some ways to get started:
      li Come out to our Civic Hack Night, to contribute to one of our projects.
      li Attend one of our upcoming events or workshops.
      li Partner with us to develop an event or sponsor a planned event.
      li Feed our civic hackers by donating food to our weekly meetings.
      li If any of the above options entice you, or if you have an idea for another way to contribute, let us know how you want to get involved.

